cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.IT 

This paper deals with the problem of improving the performance of cellular networks using reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also proposes two algorithms that use Q-learning to estimate future performance improvement rewards, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of closed loop power control and self-organizing network fault management also indicates that it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
